Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像和父亲一起住的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.41,0:03:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第55话 石之花与七宝的初恋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  该不会是假情报吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种村落会有四魂碎片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇也感受不到\N四魂碎片的气息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之还是散开来寻找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解散
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.68,0:03:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:04:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会\N想一个人去勾引女人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有妖怪的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  你这种态度对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明才刚开始找耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有妖怪的话一闻就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就是想偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪?七宝不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概跑去玩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还是小孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉  真是让人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这阵子一直不断战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔也该让他们两人独处一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住  臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不会被你们逮到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,揍扁她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你偷了我们家的柿子干对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有偷  你有看到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴  你这骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些家伙  等哥哥回来后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会好好的修理你们一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哥哥不是早就死在战场上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我父亲在他死前照顾他的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥才没有死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.81,0:05:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑蛋  小偷还敢打人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼…赢了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  狸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是狐狸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是帮助我的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要吃一半
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷来的柿子干
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来真的是这家伙不对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好厉害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫五月  你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我叫做七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝?好帅气的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲帮我取的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  你父亲是妖怪狸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐狸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是故意的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月  你有亲人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出生后不久就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我还有一个哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等他在战场立下大功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:06:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为武士后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会回来迎接我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那刚才那些小鬼在撒谎咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也会活着回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别让你看看  我的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要对它许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何愿望都会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它叫做四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说是妖怪的宝贝碎片喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.07,0:07:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么愿望\N都能实现的四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会成为武士的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥绝对不会说谎的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的吗?法师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家有妖怪盘踞着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  若没有尽早驱除的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是法师的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不需要答谢我  名主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说  各位的\N餐点与床铺已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒那家伙又在唬人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地震
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是胡扯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.25,0:08:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝你居然知道这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.39,0:09:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找这附近看起来最富裕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又在做法事的人家准没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.17,0:09:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总…总之
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到四魂碎片了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是五月吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让姐姐看看你的碎片好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会想抢走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然要抢  如果是真的的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的  只是看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  如果是真的四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就非拿走不可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来五月的愿望就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:10:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会判断的这么草率
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  笨蛋  我是大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了吧  我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.89,0:10:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  路上小心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她回去好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月  你还是不想来我们家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哥哥现正在回来的路上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  那个碎片…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  那是石之花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石之花?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是石英吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之是山上就能挖到的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不是四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是冒牌货啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.82,0:10:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月是个可怜的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥已经确定是战死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她却不愿意相信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:11:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望哥哥能快点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使我说由我们照顾她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她依然不肯离开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经和哥哥一起生活的小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.21,0:11:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然被轰出了名主的家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那小女孩可以利用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我记住!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂拥有能创造\N奈落分身的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果向真正的碎片许愿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月的哥哥就能活着回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,图形好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉!你不是在睡觉吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是帮助人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别做梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  你也知道四魂之玉的可怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是人类能使用的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.31,0:12:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  你为什么要偏袒那小女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷恋人家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的脸长得蛮可爱的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙  为了这么烂的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我迷恋她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在桔梗跟戈薇之间\N摇摆不定的你也没资格说我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去睡觉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了 你过得好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直相信!我一直相信着!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥一定会回来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少应该向她道别
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月会不会一直\N对着假碎片祈祷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我实在说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情的真相…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的愿望实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.74,0:14:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  七宝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那叫做五月的女孩那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他真的很担心她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月的哥哥早就不在人世了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她却深信假的碎片而等待着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又要多管闲事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.43,0:14:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  虽然哥哥受了一点伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥真的回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:14:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.47,0:15:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是托你和四魂碎片的福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!妖怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.09,0:15:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥要快点治好伤口\N恢复精神喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…让你吃了这么多苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后哥哥会让你很幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀…你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.48,0:15:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在名主家借宿的\N那一行人的伙伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能把那东西拿来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开五月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要做什么  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂碎片的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不就有一个吗  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:15:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种烂石头一点用都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然将实现五月愿望的碎片…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  矮子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.25,0:16:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去拿四魂碎片来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我就扭断五月的脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是你哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现出原形吧  妖怪!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐火!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这小鬼真狠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来觉得当她哥哥也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.37,0:16:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑蛋  我饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经被发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月  你先逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  我怎么能这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.28,0:17:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只能一个人骑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是五月住的小木屋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.61,0:17:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细看  是大肚子妖怪的杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少他们似乎是逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先追上七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两人一定要平安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是七宝的狐妖术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是五月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起  云母
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝在妖怪那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  走吧  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月  你一定要平安逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.06,0:18:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小女孩逃走是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.23,0:18:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,矮子  我要拿你当人质
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去抢四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你一开始就应该找我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然还刻意践踏五月的心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑蛋  我饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:19:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思  你想和我打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招  消化液
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招  爆雷筒…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子  你闹够了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.11,0:19:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的力量还是不够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能跟大家一样战斗吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  还没得到教训
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又变成奇怪的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.14,0:20:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙  你在找碴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿你试试刚领悟的爆流破
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子  你在胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将对手的妖气卷入风之伤中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再让妖气逆流的必杀剑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.17,0:20:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆流…啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶!对手的妖气太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆流破根本就用不出来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在罗哩叭唆什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.98,0:20:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太弱了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.85,0:20:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.99,0:20:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是昨晚从名主家中\N赶走的妖怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  你这次相当努力嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.01,0:21:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你解决了那只妖怪对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我  是犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪就已经被扁得很惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只妖怪知道打不过我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想利用五月吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一牵扯到四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都会遭遇不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.51,0:21:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我忘的一干二净
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才让五月碰到这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:21:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.56,0:22:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.83,0:22:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.77,0:22:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要让名主大人照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.03,0:22:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我已经知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥已经不在人世了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.95,0:22:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保重喔  五月
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.78,0:22:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能遇见你真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.66,0:22:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月  你一定要幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.09,0:22:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你一样没有父母
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.47,0:22:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我不是一个人活着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:22:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  你是不是喜欢那孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.55,0:23:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.12,0:23:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是人小鬼大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.62,0:23:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然小也是男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.29,0:23:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初恋呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.63,0:23:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.90,0:23:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  再拖拖拉拉就不理你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.89,0:23:49.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,除了真正珍贵的东西{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.04,0:24:01.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,若能全都舍弃 那该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.28,0:24:08.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,只是现实 往往是如此残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:12.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,但每当 遇到这种时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.36,0:24:17.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要紧闭双眼
